---
---
<section class="section news-section" id="news">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="glow-badge">IN THE NEWS</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Impact That <span class="text-gradient">Made Headlines</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From viral surgery moments to global recognition — stories that define a career dedicated to restoring lives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="news-list">
      <!-- Story 1: Guitar Surgeon -->
      <article class="news-item reveal">
        <div class="news-image-box">
          <video class="news-img" autoplay muted loop playsinline style="object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%;display:block;">
            <source src="/images/guitar_surgery.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="news-category">VIRAL STORY</div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-content">
          <div class="news-eyebrow">July 2017 · Global Sensation</div>
          <h3 class="news-title">🎸 "The Guitar Surgeon" — A Surgery the World Will Never Forget</h3>
          <p class="news-text">
            A talented guitarist walked into Dr. Sharan's clinic with <strong>Task-Specific Focal Hand Dystonia</strong> — every time he tried to play, his three left-hand fingers froze involuntarily. No medication worked. No therapy helped.
          </p>
          <p class="news-text">
            Dr. Sharan performed a high-stakes <strong>awake VO Thalamotomy</strong> — a pinpoint ablation of the Ventralis Oralis nucleus in the thalamus. As the circuit was released, the guitarist's frozen fingers <em>magically moved</em>. He began playing his guitar, mid-surgery, on the operating table.
          </p>
          <p class="news-text">
            His wife — allowed into the OT — filmed it on her phone. She posted it on Facebook. The video went viral worldwide, reaching millions within 24 hours. Dr. Sharan became "The Guitar Surgeon" — known around the globe.
          </p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="news-date">🏅 A Proud National Moment for India</span>
            <a href="#" class="news-link">View Full Story <span>→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Story 2: Podcast -->
      <article class="news-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="news-image-box">
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/5GtMcmgXY929lICIgBeyFhkSmI.jpg" alt="Rebooting the Brain Podcast" class="news-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="news-category">PODCAST LAUNCH</div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-content">
          <div class="news-eyebrow">Launched December 14, 2024</div>
          <h3 class="news-title">🎙️ "Rebooting the Brain" — Podcast That Puts the Mind Back in Medicine</h3>
          <p class="news-text">
            Did you know that in most Indian hospitals, a "Master Health Checkup" scans everything from the chest down — but <strong>not a single brain test</strong> is done? Dr. Sharan was deeply troubled by this blind spot.
          </p>
          <p class="news-text">
            That led to the birth of <em>Rebooting the Brain</em> — an open mic to the world. Within months, it became <strong>one of the most-watched neuroscience podcasts globally</strong>, reaching parents, patients, healers, and policy makers alike. Unfiltered. Unscripted. Uncompromising.
          </p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <div class="news-btns">
              <a href="#" class="btn-sm">Listen Now</a>
              <a href="#" class="btn-sm outline">All Episodes</a>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="news-link">The Story Behind It <span>→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Story 3: NBEC 2022 -->
      <article class="news-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="news-image-box accent-box">
          <div class="award-icon">🏆</div>
          <div class="news-category">NATIONAL WINNER</div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-content">
          <div class="news-eyebrow">NBEC 2022 · C-CAMP, Govt. of India</div>
          <h3 class="news-title">newro LOGICS — Grand Finale Winner at India's Premier Bio-Entrepreneurship Competition</h3>
          <p class="news-text">
            Out of <strong>3,000+ bio-entrepreneurs</strong> across medtech, agritech, vaccine tech, and health tech, <strong>newro LOGICS</strong> emerged as the national winner at the <strong>National Bio-Entrepreneurship Competition (NBEC) 2022</strong> — India's premier platform for biotech innovation, hosted by C-CAMP, a flagship Government of India initiative.
          </p>
          <p class="news-text">
            The platform received prize money and acclaim from top scientific leaders and innovation investors for its <em>"practical brilliance and scalable vision."</em>
          </p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="news-date">🇮🇳 Making India Proud in Innovation</span>
            <a href="#" class="news-link">About newro LOGICS <span>→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .news-section {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .glow-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .news-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .news-item {
    display: flex;
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .news-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-premium);
    background: white;
    border-color: rgba(79,70,229,0.2);
  }

  .news-image-box {
    flex: 0 0 320px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 260px;
  }

  .accent-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e1b4b 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .award-icon {
    font-size: 5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255,200,0,0.4));
  }

  .news-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .news-item:hover .news-img {
    transform: scale(1.06);
  }

  .news-category {
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    left: 18px;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    color: white;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .news-content {
    padding: 36px 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .news-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .news-title {
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .news-text {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .news-text:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .news-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .news-date {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .news-link {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-main);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: gap 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .news-link:hover {
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .news-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .btn-sm {
    padding: 8px 18px;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .btn-sm.outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
  }

  .btn-sm:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .news-image-box { flex: 0 0 260px; }
    .news-title { font-size: 1.35rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .news-item {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .news-image-box {
      flex: none;
      height: 220px;
      min-height: 220px;
    }
    .news-item:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    .news-content { padding: 28px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .news-title { font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .news-content { padding: 22px; }
    .news-image-box { height: 180px; min-height: 180px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .news-meta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .news-btns { flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }
</style>
